# Build context for docker/aca-runner/Dockerfile is this directory
# (docker/aca-runner/). Nothing here today needs to be excluded — the image
# installs a pinned `conductor-cli` release from GitHub (`pip install
# "conductor-cli @ git+https://github.com/microsoft/conductor.git@<ref>"` —
# there is no PyPI package) rather than copying repo source — but this file
# exists as the documented place to exclude local build artifacts if this
# directory ever gains any (e.g. a scratch wheel used for a pre-release
# smoke build).
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.git
.DS_Store
